<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL">&gt; Alright, this mode of Sonic Adventure has:
&gt; 4 new characters:
&gt; Kiao the hedgehog,Kitty the Echidna,Ostro, and Hero Chao Walker.Kiao is a small 10 year old hedgehog with amazing intelligence and the ability to create and expand fire,lava,etc(hot material). Kitty is a 13 year old echidna that looks remarkably like a cat. She has amazing spiritual powers like Tikal and is able to detect diamonds like Knuckles.Ostro is an female emu who hates Sonic.She can jump high and can destroy robots with her Birdie Bomber.Hero Chao Walker is a robot made for Hero Chao by Tails.It can Hover longer and farther than other robots and can fire Homing missles faster.
&gt; 3 different modes and 3 different stories:
&gt; You can pick between Adventure,Digging,and Robotics.
&gt; Then, you pick between Hero or Dark story.
&gt; Adventure is like the Sonic/Shadow stages of SA2.
&gt; Digging is like the Knuckles/Rouge stages of SA2.
&gt; Robotics is like the Tails/Eggman stages of SA2.
&gt; Adventure characters are (hero)Sonic,Kiao,(dark)Metal Sonic,and Ostro.Digging characters are(hero)Knuckles,Rouge,(dark)Ankles(see my idea of SA3) and Chaos Zero.
&gt; Robotics characters are (hero)Tails,Hero Chao Walker(dark)Eggman,and Dark Chao Walker.
&gt; Chao:
&gt; Has combined features of SA2 and SA2B and also if you raise a Hero or Dark Chao you can use it in the Chao Walkers in Robotics!
&gt; 
&gt; Tell me if you like my idea.

